dc_title_s: Digital Elevation Model (30m): Monterey County, California, 1999
dc_description_s: This raster layer contains a 30-meter seamless digital elevation model for Monterey County, California in 1999. This layer is part of a collection of data and maps containing geologic information prepared for the Monterey County General Plan Update. This layer is part of a collection describing Geology resources and constraints Monterey County, California.This dataset is intended for researchers, students, and policy makers for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data.
